The paper deals with the extension of first-order lambda calculus and its type system, which is a topic in logic and computation (cs.LO). It also involves the manipulation of vector spaces and their axioms, which falls under programming languages (cs.PL) and category theory (cs.CC). The paper also discusses the computational reasoning involved in the type system, which is related to data structures (cs.DS) and information theory (cs.IT).
